[3] Congo DR
Date: Mon 5 Apr 2004 19:12:55 -0400
From: Alfonso Rodriguez <arodriguezm@SaludFMV.org>
Source: Yahoo News, UK [edited]
<http://uk.news.yahoo.com/040405/323/eqcy7.html>

Epidemic of cholera in DR Congo
-------------------------------
In southeastern Katanga province, 51 people have died out of 1139
registered cases of cholera, Health Minister Jean Yagi Sitolo said in a
statement on Mon 5 Apr 2004.
In central Kasai Oriental province, cholera has infected 258 people, killing
8.
